Developed an interactive Power BI dashboard using Superstore sales data to analyze business performance across sales, profit, orders, customers, regions, and product categories. The dashboard provides actionable insights through dynamic visualizations, KPI cards, filters, and trend analysis to support data-driven decision-making.

Key Features
Sales and Profit Analysis
Regional Performance Tracking
Category and Sub-Category Insights
Customer Segment Analysis
Interactive Slicers and Filters
KPI Cards for Sales, Profit, and Orders
Time-Series Trend Analysis
Data Modeling and DAX Measures
Tools & Technologies
Power BI Desktop
Power Query
DAX (Data Analysis Expressions)
Data Modeling
Interactive Data Visualization
